OL,3,CMotorway re-opens after weekend
OL,4,Cclosures caused by fire
OL,6,FA major motorway in Hampshire was
OL,7,Fclosed for a second day due to a fire
OL,8,Fat a waste processing unit.
OL,10,FThe M275 in Portsmouth was shut by
OL,11,Fpolice as thick black smoke continued
OL,12,Fto drift across the motorway.
OL,14,FThe blaze broke out at around 6.30am
OL,15,Fon Saturday (6 July) at TJ Waste &
OL,16,FRecycling in Tipner.
OL,18,FThe road reopened on Sunday (7 July)
OL,19,Fat around 2.30pm.
