OL,6,FHampshire Constabulary took the
OL,7,Fdecision to close the motorway due to
OL,8,Fthe hazardous smoke which caused poor
OL,9,Fvisibility for drivers, making the
OL,10,Froad unsafe to use.
OL,12,FHampshire Search and Rescue posted
OL,13,Fthermal images of the fire from its
OL,14,Fheat-seeking drone, which was deployed
OL,15,Fto help firefighters tackle hot spots.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for TJ Waste &
OL,18,FRecycling said: "We are deeply
OL,19,Fappreciative of the work done by crews
OL,20,Ffrom Hampshire & Isle of Wight Fire
OL,21,Fand Rescue and their control room.
