OL,6,F"We also express our thanks to the
OL,7,Fpolice and city council for arranging
OL,8,Froad diversions due to the closure of
OL,9,Fthe M275 for safety reasons due to the
OL,10,Fsmoke.
OL,12,F"We also extend our gratitude to the
OL,13,Fpublic for their understanding and
OL,14,Fpatience over the weekend during this
OL,15,Funprecedented incident.
OL,17,F"TJ staff are on site, assisting
OL,18,Ffirefighters in dampening the fire
OL,19,Fwithin the building with the use of
OL,20,Four plant and equipment.
