OL,6,F"As yet, the cause of the fire is not
OL,7,Fknown. However, there is an increasing
OL,8,Ftrend of lithium batteries being
OL,9,Fdiscarded incorrectly by users.
OL,11,F"The batteries, which charge
OL,12,Felectrical devices such as mobile
OL,13,Fphones, vapes and e-bikes, can be
OL,14,Fexplosive and, due to 'thermal
OL,15,Frunaway', cannot be extinguished
OL,16,Feasily because the heat is so
OL,17,Fferocious.
